msgid "Scenario VII: Return to Lost in Time and Space"
msgstr "冒险VII：重返迷失时空"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: The Edge of the Universe, Tear Through Time, and Seth Bishop <i>(Thrall of Yog-Sothoth)</i>."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于场外：宇宙的边缘、时间缝隙、赛斯·毕晓普<i>(犹格·索托斯的奴仆)</i>。"

msgid "Replace Act 2a - \"Into the Beyond\" with the new Act 2a - \"Into the Beyond (v. II)\" from the <i>Return to Lost in Time and Space</i> encounter set."
msgstr "将场景2a - “超越领域”替换为<i>重返迷失时空</i>遭遇组中新的场景2a - “超越领域(版本二)”。"

msgid "Replace Agenda 3a - \"Breaking Through\" with the new Agenda 3a - \"Breaking Through (v. II)\" included in this encounter set."
msgstr "将密谋3a - “突破”替换为此遭遇组中新的密谋3a - “突破(版本二)”。"

msgid "Put the single-sided Realms Beyond location into play and spawn Yog-Sothoth there."
msgstr "将单面的异界领域地点放置入场，并将犹格·索托斯生成于此。"
